      • QueryEngineException

        public QueryEngineException(java.lang.String msg,
                    java.lang.String query,
                    int lineNum,
                    java.lang.String filename,
                    java.lang.Throwable cause)
        Wraps a more generic exception that may have been thrown in the SearchEngine class. Arguments contain more specific details about the exception to simplify debugging.
        Parameters:
        msg - the exception message from the throwing cause
        query - the string value of the line that caused the exception
        lineNum - the line number in the file that caused the exception
        filename - the filename that was the cause of the original exception
        cause - the wrapped lower-level exception that triggered this exception's creation
